      "description": "Wall shear stress distributions at 3500 RPM / 5 L/min compared against PIV-derived estimates from Morrison et al. (2023). Agreement within 8% at 90% of measurement locations. Validation supports adequacy of turbulence model selection for hemolysis prediction."
