      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index RH predicted vs. measured across 5 operating points. Mean absolute relative error 6.3%; maximum 11.2% at lowest flow condition. Validation metric M = 0.78 (> 0.70 threshold). Model deemed adequate for comparative worst-case identification."
