      "rationale": "Validation conducted on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — identical to COU device class. Operating envelope (2500–3500 RPM, 3–7 L/min) fully encompasses COU operating range. Blood analogue viscosity within 5% of clinical hematocrit-adjusted viscosity. Relevance assessed as high."
